235","rect":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":155,"height":39},"offset":{"x":0,"y":0},"originalSize":{"width":155,"height":39},"rotated":false,"capInsets":[18,9,27,9],"vertices":{"rawPosition":[-77.5,-19.5,0,77.5,-19.5,0,-77.5,19.5,0,77.5,19.5,0],"indexes":[0,1,2,2,1,3],"uv":[0,39,155,39,0,0,155,0],"nuv":[0,0,1,0,0,1,1,1],"minPos":{"x":-77.5,"y":-19.5,"z":0},"maxPos":{"x":77.5,"y":19.5,"z":0}},"packable":true,"pixelsToUnit":100,"pivot":{"x":0.5,"y":0.5},"meshType":0}],[5],0,[0],[5],[6]],[[{"name":"tablr","rect":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":1000,"height":575},"offset":{"x":0,"y":0},"originalSize":{"width":1000,"height":575},"rotated":false,"capInsets":[0,0,0,0],"vertices":{"rawPosition":[-500,-287.5,0,500,-287.5,0,-500,287.5,0,500,287.5,0],"indexes":[0,1,2,2,1,3],"uv":[0,575,1000,575,0,0,1000,0],"nuv":[0,0,1,0,0,1,1,1],"minPos":{"x":-500,"y":-287.5,"z":0},"maxPos":{"x":500,"y":287.5,"z":0}},"packable":true,"pixelsToUnit":100,"pivot":{"x":0.5,"y":0.5},"meshType":0}],[5],0,[0],[5],[7]],[[[45,"GalleryDataCSV","﻿ID,Category,CategoryDisplayName,CharacterCode,Name,Age,Ethnicity,Title,GangName,Gang,Bio,Role\r\n1,EMERGENCY_PERSONNEL,Emergency Personnel,SHERIFF_HARLAN,Sheriff Harlan,52,American,Sheriff,None,NONE,\"Sheriff Harlan is an old-fashioned, no nonsense kind of man. He says what he thinks and he does what he says. He's here to uphold the law and gladly reminds you of it. You can get far with Sheriff Harlan, to a certain degree. Show him respect and he'll treat you fairly. Take him for a fool and you just might find yourself in the back of his vehicle, handcuffed and sorry. But by then, it'll be too late.\",\"Sheriff Harlan will appear during the more serious incidents in Adrenaline City. If authority is needed, you can bet he will be there to show it. You might be required to help Sheriff Harlan with a thing or two, to get into his good graces, but it'll be wise for you to stay as far away from the law as possible.\"\r\n2,EMERGENCY_PERSONNEL,Emergency Personnel,SHERIFF_CONRAD,Sheriff's Deputy Conrad,28,American,Sheriff's Deputy,None,NONE,\"Conrad is your average all American good guy. He looks up to Sheriff Harlan a lot, and is incorruptible, as straight as an arrow and as helpful as he is friendly. Unless he's forced to be otherwise. Then Conrad may as well be your worst enemy. He upholds the law to the best of his abilities, but has a soft spot for anything that makes sense to him. You may find a friend in him.\",\"Any regular crime that is committed, accident, breaking, theft or otherwise and you can expect Conrad to be first at the scene. He'll not provide you with any missions of your own, but may sometimes tag along if he's needed for something related to criminal activity.\"\r\n3,EMERGENCY_PERSONNEL,Emergency Personnel,EMT_JESSY,Jessica (Jessy) The EMT,29,American,Emergency Medical Technician,None,NONE,\"Jessy doesn't play around, because she's got no time to waste. With any accident or worse, she will be right there, barking orders to save lives. She doesn't care who it is or why they are hurt. All she wants is for the person to make it. She's very direct, friendly when she can be, but above all, a professional. You'd do well to listen to her. Or you might get an earful.\",\"Jessy will always be there when someone's hurt. She may require you quite often to help her out, as she's always busy saving lives. Help Jessy as much as you can and she'll always be there for you. She does kind of remind you of someone though, but you can't quite place it yet. Who is she, really? What's her story?\"\r\n4,EMERGENCY_PERSONNEL,Emergency Personnel,DOCTOR_SANJAY_YADAV,Doctor Sanjay Yadav,30,Indian,Doctor/Surgeon,None,NONE,\"Doctor Yadav is a medical professional and very good at his job. If a life ends up in his hands, it's likely that life will be saved. He's friendly, understanding, forthcoming and always respectful.\",\"If someone got seriously hurt, there's only one man for the job. Doctor Yadav will make sure they are taken care of. You may sometimes get a mission to help out the Doctor, when there's really no other way. But how far is the Doctor willing to go, to make sure lives are saved? Sometimes, you wonder yourself.\"\r\n5,EMERGENCY_PERSONNEL,Emergency Personnel,FIRE_MARSHALL_STEVE,Fire Marshall Steve,34,American,Fire Marshall,None,NONE,Fire Marshall Steve has no time for chit chat. Do as you're told and he might save you and anyone else in need of saving. He'd literally run into a burning building if there's even a 5% chance that he'll come out of it alive.,\"Fire Marshall Steve will be there when things are burning and lives are in danger. He might need your help with an odd mission here and there, but always for the good of Adrenaline City.\"\r\n6,BRICKERS_BIKER_GANG,Bricker's Biker Gang,BRICKER,Bricker (The Brick),41,American,Leader,Bricker's Biker Gang,BBG,\"Being a biker is a lifestyle. But it isn't easy. Bricker however, makes it look flawless. Most people think that bikers can't drive cars, and Bricker thinks that's stupid. He's also happy to prove you wrong. Bricker is in many ways like a brick. He's tough, stone cold and rough. Does that make him unfriendly? Only when he has to be. Otherwise Bricker is a straight shooter with little feelings or concerns about others. You stay out of his way, or he goes out of his way to make way.\",\"Bricker says it how it is. And how it is, is how it's going to be. Don't like it? Tough luck, because whatever Bricker says, goes. No ifs ands or buts. Bricker will tell you what to do, when to do it, and if you need to know, why to do it. But he doesn't always have time to. So he's not the only one who bosses you around.\"\r\n7,BRICKERS_BIKER_GANG,Bricker's Biker Gang,RICKY_THE_RIVER,Ricky The River,38,American,Lieutenant,Bricker's Biker Gang,BBG,\"Ricky is a completely different person than Brick, yet he somehow managed to become his trusted associate and hands out orders like no other. Ricky takes care and care takes. You got a problem? Ricky's got you. You need a problem solved? Ricky will take care of it. You mess with Ricky? You could require stitches afterwards.\",Many of the missions for the Brickers Gang will be handled by Ricky. Do as he says and do it well and you just might make it.\r\n8,BRICKERS_BIKER_GANG,Bricker's Biker Gang,BRUTUS_BOVINE,Brutus Bovine,45,American,Security,Bricker's Biker Gang,BBG,\"Brutus is a lapdog. It's painful to say out loud, but that's the reality. And he doesn't mind his reality. Brutus was hit over the head more times than a tennis ball and it has left some marks. But for all his simplicity, Brutus lives up to his name. He's insanely strong, barely feels pain, never complains and ALWAYS comes through. What Brutus doesn't know, won't hurt him.\",\"Brutus goes where he's told, does what he's told and talks when he's told. Brutus won't give you many missions, but he's there when you need him to be. And what's the deal with his Aunt Caroline? Why does she matter so much?\"\r\n9,BRICKERS_BIKER_GANG,Bricker's Biker Gang,SAMANTHA_STONE,Samantha Stone,29,American,Henchman,Bricker's Biker Gang,BBG,\"If names were clichÃ©s, Samantha would be on top. Samantha is Brick's girlfriend. But just because she sleeps with Brick, doesn't mean she gets to give orders. Samantha knows her place and stays in her lane. She's sassy, but fun to be around.\",\"Samantha might get you in trouble on more occasions than you'd like. She has a lot going on and requires a lot of attention. Sometimes, the not so nice kind. Help Samantha deal with problems and you could get praise from Brick for your efforts. Because sometimes even he can't handle her.\"\r\n10,BRICKERS_BIKER_GANG,Bricker's Biker Gang,CLETUS,Cletus,19,American,Specific Character,Bricker's Biker Gang,BBG,\"Cletus is your run of the mill hillbilly. A redneck. A moron. And because of his low IQ, he often gets himself into trouble. He doesn't even remember his own last name. Maybe that has something to do with the fact that Cletus is a teenager, but that's not the point. Cletus always tries too hard and fails every time. Can there be any hope for his future?\",\"Cletus is always almost an adult. As if that will change anything for him. And because of that, he always wants to do adult stuff. Because he might as well be, seeing as he almost is. Right? Missions involving Cletus are a bit strange and unusual, but mostly fun. He will rely on you to increase his success rate.\"\r\n11,BRICKERS_BIKER_GANG,Bricker's Biker Gang,TONY_THE_TECHNICIAN,Tony the Technician,26,American,Special Character,Bricker's Biker Gang,BBG,\"Tony the Tech handles all of the Bricker's mechanical needs. And because of this, he has a lot of things to consider and worry about. Because a faulty bike is the same as no bike. And Tony can't afford to be responsible for fatal mechanical issues with any of the bikes. So, he constantly thinks of ways to improve and get better.\",\"Missions from Tony will come often and involve a lot. No mission is easy, but the rewards will be definitely worth it. Bikes that need to compete on the streets with cars, better be the best bikes out there. Helping Tony means helping the Bricker's Biker Gang. And helping the Brickers, is good for everyone. Because who doesn't like bikes? Right?\"\r\n12,CITY_CHARACTER,City Characters,BRIAN_THE_SUPPLIER,Brian The Supplier,29,Canadian,The Supplier,None,NONE,\"Brian is your run of the mill supplier. Straight to the point and always ready to make a deal, Brian drops off and charges your for his services. Not much is to be said or done.\",\"Sometimes you require supplies for missions. But you don't always have what you need. That's where Brian comes in. He can get you almost anything your need. But what you order, might not always be what you need.\"\r\n13,CITY_CHARACTER,City Characters,EVENT_ORGANIZER,The Event Organizer,28,American,The Event Organizer,None,NONE,\"Loud, excited, informative!\",The Event Organizer will appear whenever there is any type of Event. And he'll happily announce them to you.\r\n14,CITY_CHARACTER,City Characters,DARREN_THE_DELIVERY_GUY,Darren The Delivery Guy,26,American,The Delivery Guy,None,NONE,Not much to say about the friendly delivery guy. Service with a smile!,You'll often need to receive a delivery. Darren will be there to delivery it straight to your doorstep. So you'll be seeing a lot of this guy in game.\r\n15,CITY_CHARACTER,City Characters,MR_FRANCO,Mr. Franco,30,Italian American,The Hotel Manager,None,NONE,Mr. Franco embodies Customer Service. Any stay at his Hotel will be met with a courteous and service oriented approach.,Mr. Franco will always be there to greet you if you need to stay in his Hotel.\r\n16,CITY_CHARACTER,City Characters,STANLEY,Stanley,43,American,The Gas Station Clerk,None,NONE,\"Quiet, simple and efficient.\",Stanley will get involved for any fuel related query.\r\n17,CITY_CHARACTER,City Characters,HEATHER,Heather,25,American,The Adrenaline Junkie,None,NONE,\"Crazy, wild, outrageous, fun, exciting and over the top. Heather is just too much fun too handle.\",\"Sometimes you need to just break away from all the regular stuff and do something crazy. Well, Heather is right there to give you exactly that. Whether it's jumping from a helicopter, a bicycle chase, rollerblades, a quad bike, you name it, Heather will find a way to do something crazy with you. You know, for fun!\"\r\n18,CITY_CHARACTER,City Characters,SEBASTIAN_CONTRERAS,SebastiÃ¡n Contreras,44,Spanish,The Restaurant Owner,None,NONE,\"A very funny, very friendly and very service oriented man, SebastiÃ¡n's only objective is to make sure you're entertained and well fed.\",\"You'll sometimes have to meet some high class people in Adrenaline City. No better place to do so than in SebastiÃ¡n's Restaurant. He'll provide the food and the entertainment, while you discuss business.\"\r\n19,CITY_CHARACTER,City Characters,BARTEK_THE_CUSTOMIZER,Bartek The Customizer,37,Polish,The Customizer,None,NONE,Bartek will take any request you have with enthusiasm and a smile! No customization is too great or too complicated for him!,\"Whether you need to customize an item, a car part or an entire car, Bartek can do it all! Responsible for the Customization Feature in game, once you can finally customize, you'll want to put him to immediate use, because after he's done, you'll like what he did!\"\r\n20,CITY_CHARACTER,City Characters,SYLVESTER,Sylvester,31,American,The Car Wash Owner,None,NONE,\"Excited and friendly, Sylvester is always happy to make your ride shine just that much brighter.\",\"Want to increase your Shine or Bling stats, a trip to the Car Wash will make heads turn and ensure none of your rides go unnoticed.\"\r\n21,CITY_CHARACTER,City Characters,BUNWI,Bunwi,10,Jamaican American,The Gifter,None,NONE,\"Bunwi, meaning The Gift, is a kid of the streets. He sees more than you know and knows more than you see. It's easy to underestimate him due to his size and age. But he's always there to help you, and a bit of a wisecrack.\",\"Bunwi will provide you with missions and the rewards are always worth it. Responsible for Gift Boxes that can be obtained in various ways, Bunwi will make your stay in Adrenaline City worth it, all by himself.\"\r\n"]],0,0,[],[],[]],[[{"name":"button","rect":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":500,"height":113},"offset":{"x":0,"y":0},"originalSize":{"width":500,"height":113},"rotated":false,"capInsets":[0,0,0,0],"vertices":{"rawPosition":[-250,-56.5,0,250,-56.5,0,-250,56.5,0,250,56.5,0],"indexes":[0,1,2,2,1,3],"uv":[0,113,500,113,0,0,500,0],"nuv":[0,0,1,0,0,1,1,1],"minPos":{"x":-250,"y":-56.5,"z":0},"maxPos":{"x":250,"y":56.5,"z":0}},"packable":true,"pixelsToUnit":100,"pivot":{"x":0.5,"y":0.5},"meshType":0}],[5],0,[0],[5],[8]],[[{"name":"icon gallery","rect":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":50,"height":44},"offset":{"x":0,"y":0},"originalSize":{"width":50,"height":44},"rotated":false,"capInsets":[0,0,0,0],"vertices":{"rawPosition":[-25,-22,0,25,-22,0,-25,22,0,25,22,0],"indexes":[0,1,2,2,1,3],"uv":[0,44,50,44,0,0,50